mods:titleInfo.mods:title: Charles W. Leffingwell bunk house (Whittier, Calif.)

Bunk-house for C. W. Leffingwell Esqr. at Whittier, Cal, Detail of seat in front and end elevations; elevations of south side of stairs, east side of stairs showint wainscot in dining room (same wainscot in living room); details of chimney and galvanized vent -- north side, west side; detail of splice for 8" x 6" plates; outer wall section with exterior and interior elevations of windows; details of vents in gable ends; detail of joint in sills; north elevation; south elevation : Sheet no. 5,

mods:mods.mods:note: Gift of Jean Murray Bangs) Mrs. Harwell Hamilton Harris), 1960; formerly the collection of Charles Sumner Greene.

mods:location.mods:physicalLocation: Avery Architectural & Fine Arts Library, Columbia University
